OL,3,CTamworth FC to complete US takeover
OL,5,FA United States consortium is
OL,6,Ffinalising a deal to buy National
OL,7,FLeague football club Tamworth FC.
OL,9,FTalks have been ongoing for months and
OL,10,Fare now understood to be just weeks
OL,11,Faway from completion.
OL,13,FAs reported by TalkSport, members of
OL,14,Fthe group were at Tamworth's 5-1 win
OL,15,Fagainst Braintree on Saturday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
