OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777356312
OL,3,CTamworth FC to complete US takeover
OL,5,FClub insiders are so confident about
OL,6,Fthe financial might of their
OL,7,Fprospective buyers that they hope for
OL,8,Fa Wrexham-style rise through the
OL,9,Fleagues, but with a more realistic
OL,10,Ftimeframe.
OL,12,FThe Lambs famously took Tottenham
OL,13,FHotspur to extra-time in last season's
OL,14,FFA Cup third round but have never
OL,15,Fplayed in the top four tiers of
OL,16,FEnglish football.
OL,18,FThey believe this investment will take
OL,19,Fthem to that level for the first time
OL,20,Fin their history.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
