OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777356312
OL,3,CTamworth FC to complete US takeover
OL,5,FPlans are already being drawn up to
OL,6,Fdevelop the club's infrastructure and
OL,7,Fstadium.
OL,9,FThe new investors are said to be
OL,10,Ffocused on having a positive impact on
OL,11,Fthe town and community.
OL,13,FThe identity of the new owners is
OL,14,Fbeing kept secret for now.
OL,16,FWhile they aren't famous names, they
OL,17,Fare in Real Estate and we're told have
OL,18,Fa number of high net worth individuals
OL,19,Fbehind them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
