OL,3,CTamworth FC to complete US takeover
OL,5,FTamworth's record-breaking goalkeeper
OL,6,Fon heroes, and why so many footballers
OL,7,Flove golf
OL,9,FThey are the latest Midlands football
OL,10,Fclub targeted by American investment.
OL,12,FBirmingham City, West Bromwich Albion
OL,13,Fand Walsall all have American owners.
OL,15,FShrewsbury Town are also reportedly in
OL,16,Ftalks with a US-based consortium.
